Description: A lightweight interface to 'Stan' <https://mc-stan.org>.
    The 'CmdStanR' interface is an alternative to 'RStan' that calls the command line interface 
    for compilation and running algorithms instead of interfacing with C++ via 'Rcpp'.
    Methods are provided for conveniently reading the results into R.
